Day 73: Jenkins Scheduled Jobs

Date: November 15, 2025
Overview
Automated jobs using cron-style scheduling.
Key Concepts Learned

Cron syntax in Jenkins
Build triggers
Poll SCM vs scheduled builds
Time zone considerations

Configuration
# Every day at 2 AM
H 2 * * *

# Every 15 minutes
H/15 * * * *

# Weekly on Sunday
H 0 * * 0

Challenges Faced
Understanding Jenkins cron syntax (H for hash distribution) vs standard cron.
